.TH btctax-config 1  btctax "btctax manual"
.SH NAME
config \- Show or set projection config (TP8 fee treatment / pre\-2025 lot method / forward method)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBconfig\fR [\fB\-\-set\-fee\-treatment\fR] [\fB\-\-set\-pre2025\-method\fR] [\fB\-\-attest\-pre2025\-method\fR] [\fB\-\-set\-forward\-method\fR] [\fB\-\-exchange\fR] [\fB\-\-effective\-from\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Show or set projection config (TP8 fee treatment / pre\-2025 lot method / forward method)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-set\-fee\-treatment\fR \fI<SET_FEE_TREATMENT>\fR

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
c
.IP \(bu 2
b
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-set\-pre2025\-method\fR \fI<SET_PRE2025_METHOD>\fR

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
fifo
.IP \(bu 2
lifo
.IP \(bu 2
hifo
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-attest\-pre2025\-method\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-set\-forward\-method\fR \fI<SET_FORWARD_METHOD>\fR
§A.5(a): append a MethodElection decision (the forward standing order). Not a flag mutation — this is an event in the ledger. Use \-\-effective\-from to set the date (default: today / the decision\*(Aqs made\-date)
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
fifo
.IP \(bu 2
lifo
.IP \(bu 2
hifo
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-exchange\fR \fI<EXCHANGE>\fR
§A.5(a) per\-ACCOUNT scope for \-\-set\-forward\-method (IRS 2025+ per\-account rule): exchange:PROVIDER:ACCOUNT (the canonical wallet grammar). Omit for a GLOBAL election (the existing behavior). Only exchange accounts are electable (a method election is a brokerage\-account concept; self:LABEL is rejected). The account MUST already exist in the vault — an unknown/typo\*(Aqd account is rejected LOUDLY so it can\*(Aqt create a dead election
.TP
\fB\-\-effective\-from\fR \fI<EFFECTIVE_FROM>\fR
Effective\-from date for \-\-set\-forward\-method (YYYY\-MM\-DD). Defaults to made\-date
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
